<p>There are some templates intended to make bookshelves more attractive.
</p>
<ul><li> <a href="/wiki/Template:Ebook" title="Template:Ebook">Template:Ebook</a> Prints a <a href="//www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/12345" class="extiw" title="ebook:12345">link to the ebook page</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/File:BookIcon.png" class="image"><img alt="BookIcon.png" src="//www.gutenberg.org/w/images/9/92/BookIcon.png" width="16" height="16" /></a> and puts a small book icon to the right.</li>
