Something like "Featured Bookshelf category of the month: <a href="/wiki/Science_Fiction_(Bookshelf)" title="Science Fiction (Bookshelf)">Science Fiction (Bookshelf)</a>. A good place to feature the <a href="/wiki/Christmas_(Bookshelf)" title="Christmas (Bookshelf)">Christmas (Bookshelf)</a> in December. <a href="/wiki/User:Robert_Marquardt" title="User:Robert Marquardt">Robert Marquardt</a> 11:23, 20 January 2007 (EST)
