<dl><dd><dl><dd><dl><dd>No problem with that. It just reduces the slavery section on Racism to a crosslink to Slavery. Can you rename the Holocaust bookshelf? <a href="/wiki/User:Robert_Marquardt" title="User:Robert Marquardt">Robert Marquardt</a> 07:32, 28 January 2007 (EST)</dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
