<dl><dd><dl><dd><dl><dd> I see no problem. You can create as many bookshelves as you like. I think we will keep the Racism bookshelf for now and see if it flies (ie if it gets improved). You now know that such a controversial bookshelf needs needs better planning. Best post it in a more mature state than the Racism bookshelf. Alternatively create it as an orphaned page (no links to it and no inclusion in the Bookshelf Category) and write something about your intentions on its talk page. <a href="/wiki/User:Robert_Marquardt" title="User:Robert Marquardt">Robert Marquardt</a> 14:12, 28 January 2007 (EST)</dd></dl></dd></dl></dd></dl>
